{"id":4860,"date":"2021-12-09T05:22:52","date_gmt":"2021-12-09T05:22:52","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/?p=4860"},"modified":"2025-04-22T08:52:32","modified_gmt":"2025-04-22T08:52:32","slug":"top-javascript-frameworks-list-comparison","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/top-javascript-frameworks-list-comparison\/","title":{"rendered":"10 Most Popular JavaScript Frameworks List"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When it comes to Web Development, JavaScript frameworks are one of the most favored platforms for developers &amp; businesses in today&#8217;s time. Possibly, you have had a chance to experiment with one or two of the popular JavaScript Frameworks too.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">However, somewhere in your mind, you are still a little unsure about the best one to devote yourself to mastering or suggest your developer opt for your next web development project.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This is quite obvious. JavaScript is moving at a breakneck pace and there is constant pressure to add new skills to your repository. In order to do that, knowing and understanding more of the top JavaScript Frameworks in today&#8217;s time is necessary. After thorough voting by 300+ developers at invertio, we shortlisted a few of them.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Here these are:<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_From_AngularJS_20_to_Angular_8\"><\/span>1) From AngularJS 2.0 to Angular 8<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>A few years ago, Google initiated Angular, a framework that is visionary of future changes in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/app-development\/why-api-development-crucial-modern-applications\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">web APIs<\/a> and is receptive to it. After learning from their experience in Angular 1, they created Angular 2 and made a great improvement.<\/p>\n<p>As a long-term vision, like what Google did with the Android platform, Google points to the web platform now with Angular and every six months will launch a major version of Angular.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">After the most awaited official release of AngularJS 2.0, the popularity of the framework has reached a new level in today&#8217;s time. However, this is still a risky decision to jump to the new version if you are not so sure. Let us help your decision with this flowchart-<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4861 size-full\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1.png.webp\" alt=\"angularJS 2 or 1 Top JavaScript Frameworks\" width=\"746\" height=\"766\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1.png.webp 746w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1.png-292x300.webp 292w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1.png-451x463.webp 451w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1-600x616.png.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1-300x308.png.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/angular2-or-1-150x154.png.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 746px) 100vw, 746px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Credit: <a href=\"https:\/\/daveceddia.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">daveceddia.com<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p>In fact, this is the best time to learn Angular. Angular 4 is an improvement in Angular 2, but a total rewrite of AngularJS. It has a completely different architecture. The characteristics that distinguish Angular 4 from the previous angular versions include the following:<\/p>\n<p>-&gt; Compatibility with Typescript 2.1+<br \/>\n-&gt; Improve nglf and * ngFor<br \/>\n-&gt; HTTP<br \/>\n-&gt; Animation package<br \/>\n-&gt; Router<br \/>\n-&gt; New SystemJS plugin<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Whatever the conclusion you come to, you must admit that AngularJS (maintained by Google) has the capacity to build web applications like no other. With a rapid development pace, easy code integration, readiness for unit testing AngulatJS can certainly be your choice for the next project.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<div class=\"cust-secton1 padd-all margin-40\">\n    <div class=\"dis-flex\">\n    <div class=\"colleft\">\n    <div class=\"pb-heading\">Choose Your JavaScript Weapon!<\/div>\n    <p>Learn about the most popular frameworks shaping modern web development. <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"colrit\">\n    <div class=\"text-center btn-container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/contact?utm_source=Web_blog&amp;utm_medium=GB&amp;utm_id=Contactus\" class=\"banner-btn\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_self\">Contact Us <i class=\"cusarrow-icon\"><\/i><\/a><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<hr \/>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_ReactJS\"><\/span>2) ReactJS<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">One of the other popular JavaScript Frameworks in today&#8217;s time is ReactJS again maintained by a reputed brand Facebook.\u00a0 Be it&#8217;s the ability to perform well in SEO (surprisingly being part of JS family), Simpler JSX, Virtual DOM, or powerful JavaScript library, ReactJS is a developer&#8217;s choice to build dynamic &amp; high-traffic web applications.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4863\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX.png.webp\" alt=\"Top javascript frameworks easy React JSX\" width=\"978\" height=\"291\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX.png.webp 978w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX-300x89.png.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX.png-768x229.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX.png-480x143.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX-600x179.png.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-easy-React-JSX-150x45.png.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 978px) 100vw, 978px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">However, while comparing with AngularJS, ReactJS falls short in testing simplicity and component structure. Also needless to say, this does not make ReactJS to fall short from AngularJS.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For detailed comparison:<a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/angularjs-vs-reactjs-suits-better\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> AngularJS vs ReactJS: What\u2019s good for your business?<\/a><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Meteorjs_top_JavaScript_frameworks_list\"><\/span>3) <a href=\"https:\/\/www.meteor.com\/\">Meteor.js\u00a0<\/a><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">top JavaScript frameworks list<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">JavaScript is used as the universal scripting language in browsers on the client side. Using it on the back-end as well to save time and build expertise is one of the major ideas behind Meteor.js.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hence, front-end developers can also work on the back-end comfortably with Meteor without switching context between Ruby\/Java\/Python\/PHP\/ and whatnot JavaScript. It gives the flexibility to use &#8220;one language everywhere&#8221; and that makes it different from other JavaScript frameworks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Also, Meteor is perfect for those who want to build real-time web apps. All of the app\u2019s layers from the database to template update automatically. This is how it works-<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4866\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks.png.webp\" alt=\"Meteorjs realtime Top Javascript frameworks\" width=\"823\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks.png.webp 1121w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks-300x106.png.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks.png-768x271.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks.png-1024x361.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks.png-480x169.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks-600x211.png.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Meteorjs-realtime-Top-Javascript-frameworks-150x53.png.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 823px) 100vw, 823px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hence, user does not need to refresh the page to see the updates. Just like what you see after commenting on a Linkedin post.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Also Read\u00a0 &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/how-good-is-java-for-your-web-application-development\/\">How Good Is Java For Your Web Application Development?<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_NodeJS\"><\/span>4)<a href=\"https:\/\/nodejs.org\/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Node.JS\u00a0<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The main idea of Node.js is to use non-blocking, event-driven I\/O to remain lightweight and efficient in the face of data-intensive real-time apps that run across distributed devices.\u00a0 In simple words, Node.JS is used for specific reasons to fill out particular needs.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4873\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features.jpg.webp\" alt=\"node features\" width=\"806\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features.jpg.webp 1065w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features-300x130.jpg.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features.jpg-768x332.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features.jpg-1024x443.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features.jpg-480x208.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features-600x260.jpg.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/node-features-150x65.jpg.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 806px) 100vw, 806px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">It helps build scalable and fast network applications, as it\u2019s capable of handling a large number of simultaneous connections with high throughput, which brings out high scalability. If you want an entire JavaScript environment fully featured with all the tools, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/node-js-development-company-india\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Node.js development<\/a> can be ideal for you.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><div class=\"cust-secton1 padd-all margin-40\">\n    <div class=\"dis-flex\">\n    <div class=\"colleft\">\n    <div class=\"pb-heading\">Don't Settle for Average Code<\/div>\n    <p>Discover how our insights can elevate your development strategies. <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"colrit\">\n    <div class=\"text-center btn-container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/contact?utm_source=Web_blog&amp;utm_medium=GB&amp;utm_id=Contactus\" class=\"banner-btn\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_self\">Get Free Consultation <i class=\"cusarrow-icon\"><\/i><\/a><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_TensorflowJS\"><\/span>5) <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/tensorflow\/tensorflow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TensorflowJS<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Some amazing frameworks like Tensorflow.js allow you to develop Artificial Intelligence applications easily at a faster pace. You can build intuitive and innovative Data Flow Graphs, complex computations, OCR, ICR with the help of Google\u2019s Open-Source Software Library TensorFlow.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/hire-developers\/hire-tensorflow-developers?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=tensorflow.js-4860&amp;utm_campaign=SMEs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tensorflow<\/a> is the only framework based on JavaScript that is enabled with deep learning and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">machine learning development<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Mithriljs\"><\/span>6) Mithril.js<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23534\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png-300x134.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png-768x342.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png-1024x456.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png-1536x684.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/screenshot-mithril.js.org-2022.01.20-14_59_06.png-480x214.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mithril.js has a few similar features to React.js. Mithril gives you hierarchical MVC components and safe-by-default templates with an intelligent DOM difference checking for high-performance rendering just like React. Moreover, Customizable data binding and URL routing are two of the impressive features of Mithril.js.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_PolymerJS\"><\/span>7) Polymer.JS<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Polymer is another JavaScript framework from Google. There is no doubt that the joy for developers in Polymer is much lesser than React.js still, there are many improvements made recently.\u00a0 The material design components that come with Polymer have a very high quality.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"align-center wp-image-4872 aligncenter\" style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer.png.webp\" alt=\"material component and polymer\" width=\"1007\" height=\"444\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer.png.webp 1360w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer-300x132.png.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer.png-768x339.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer.png-1024x452.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer.png-480x212.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer-600x265.png.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/material-component-and-polymer-150x66.png.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1007px) 100vw, 1007px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moreover, Polymer has web components that are part of the HTML standard which promises longer existence than ReactJS. Hence, there is a low chance for Polymer to get replaced in the future by another framework.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8_Vuejs\"><\/span>8) <a href=\"https:\/\/vuejs.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vue.js<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>After using Vue.js for a while, we decided to add it to this most popular JavaScript frameworks list in today&#8217;s time as well. There are a few reasons for that. We saw, in many cases, Vue.js is replacing Angular.<\/p>\n<p>It is a lightweight library with two-way data binding and virtual DOM that doesn&#8217;t confuse you with tons of things and helps you with just what you need to develop a web app.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5064\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js.png.webp\" alt=\"Top javascript frameworks vue js\" width=\"793\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js.png.webp 1600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js-300x159.png.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js.png-768x408.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js.png-1024x544.webp 1024w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js.png-1536x816.webp 1536w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js.png-480x255.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js-600x319.png.webp 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/10\/Top-javascript-frameworks-vue-js-150x80.png.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 793px) 100vw, 793px\" \/><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<div class=\"cust-secton1 padd-all margin-40\">\n    <div class=\"dis-flex\">\n    <div class=\"colleft\">\n    <div class=\"pb-heading\">Maximize Your App's Potential! <\/div>\n    <p>Extend the longevity of your applications with our expert maintenance. <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"colrit\">\n    <div class=\"text-center btn-container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/contact?utm_source=Web_blog&amp;utm_medium=GB&amp;utm_id=Contactus\" class=\"banner-btn\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_self\">Get Consultation Now! <i class=\"cusarrow-icon\"><\/i><\/a><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<hr \/>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"9_Aurelia\"><\/span>9) <a href=\"http:\/\/aurelia.io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Aurelia<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>The new kid in the block of Top JavaScript frameworks in today&#8217;s time is Aurelia. This framework uses <a title=\"Go to ES6 on wikipedia.org\" href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/ECMAScript#ES6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ES2016<\/a> where you can code better with object-oriented techniques. If you are using Angular 2 and are not satisfied then you can switch to Aurelia with lesser codes.\u00a0 If you are new to this framework you can watch this video<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"10_Express_Js\"><\/span>10) <a href=\"https:\/\/expressjs.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Express Js<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9909\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/1_uPL1uCtLBRSk6akPL2hNzg.jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Javascript frameworks\" width=\"629\" height=\"363\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/1_uPL1uCtLBRSk6akPL2hNzg.jpeg.webp 766w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/1_uPL1uCtLBRSk6akPL2hNzg.jpeg-300x173.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/1_uPL1uCtLBRSk6akPL2hNzg.jpeg-480x277.webp 480w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/1_uPL1uCtLBRSk6akPL2hNzg-600x346.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/02\/1_uPL1uCtLBRSk6akPL2hNzg-640x369.jpeg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Among JavaScript frameworks, if t